{"title":"前言","date":"2022-05-10T12:46:22.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2022年5月10日","L":"2022/05/10","MM-DD":"05-10"},"thumbnail":"/images/hello.jpg","link":"post/page1","comments":true,"updated":"2022-06-05T14:41:53.795Z","content":"<h2 id=\"关于博客\">关于博客<a title=\"#关于博客\" href=\"#关于博客\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"概述\">概述<a title=\"#概述\" href=\"#概述\"></a></h3>\n<p>搭博客一直鸽了好久，总算在五一假期下决心建好了。我选择的是<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/\" target=\"_blank\">Hexo</a>静态博客，部署到了GitHub Page上，整个过程下来只有域名需要花钱。主题是<a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">inside</a>，评论系统采用了简洁轻量的<a href=\"https://waline.js.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Waline</a>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"愿景\">愿景<a title=\"#愿景\" href=\"#愿景\"></a></h3>\n<p>博客，首先是给自己看的，知道这个博客的人并不多。对我个人而言，这里可以记录生活点滴，写写随想，也可以当做知识库，记记笔记。自已没有多深的文学素养，写不出精美的文章，也不是什么技术佬，写不出清晰条理的教程，只是胡写一通，乱写一气。</p>\n<h3 id=\"create-a-new-post\">Create a new post<a title=\"#create-a-new-post\" href=\"#create-a-new-post\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;  # 三种布局layout：post、page、draft，默认为post</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"front-matter\">Front-matter<a title=\"#front-matter\" href=\"#front-matter\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">title:</span><br><span class=\"line\">date:</span><br><span class=\"line\">updated:</span><br><span class=\"line\">comments:</span><br><span class=\"line\">tags:</span><br><span class=\"line\">categories:</span><br><span class=\"line\">layout:</span><br><span class=\"line\">permalink:</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 缩略图</span><br><span class=\"line\">thumbnail：</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 置顶</span><br><span class=\"line\">sticky: 1</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 全文加密</span><br><span class=\"line\">secret:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"高考","link":"post/page2"},"plink":"http://tianyu13.cn/post/page1/","toc":[{"id":"关于博客","title":"关于博客","index":"1","children":[{"id":"概述","title":"概述","index":"1.1"},{"id":"愿景","title":"愿景","index":"1.2"},{"id":"create-a-new-post","title":"Create a new post","index":"1.3"},{"id":"front-matter","title":"Front-matter","index":"1.4"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"2022年5月10日","author":"Shang","link":"<a href=\"http://tianyu13.cn/post/page1/\" title=\"前言\">http://tianyu13.cn/post/page1/</a>"},"reading_time":"236 字约 2 分钟"}